Games-Scoreboard

Perl project to manage and manipulate scoreboard, players and scores.



INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

DEPENDENCIES

Mouse;
Mouse::Util::TypeConstraints;
DateTime;
DateTime::Format::ISO8601;



